# Digrano-_website-
Di Grano is a cozy brunch spot on Wilkinson Road, Freetown—premium food, all‑day breakfast, and laid‑back service from 9 AM to 10 PM. Think banana‑pancake mornings, fried‑rice lunches, and coffee at the counter, all in a warm, sign‑lit interior.
